{
 "name": "RPlog_Positions_of_Power",
 "title": "Positions of Power",
 "summary": "In the interrogation suite of the Star Destroyer Nemesis, the captured smuggler Jaspar Andromidus -- run down after his freighter Hirakiis was caught defying the Imperial blockade of Caspia -- is questioned by a coldly methodical ISB agent. Jaspar parries with defiant wit, insisting he is a mere hauler who asks no questions, until the agent has stormtroopers pin him and inject a truth serum. Under the drug, Jaspar reveals his short-lived, money-only association with the Rebels, his voice-only contact, and a hazy memory of an ambassador, ultimately identifying Ambrosia Delgard from a recording. The agent, unsatisfied without positive identification of his co-conspirators, deems the confession insufficient to spare him, leaving Jaspar's fate grim.",
